  IS_STRING = /^['"]/;

  utility = function(name) {
    var ref;
    ref = "__" + name;
    Scope.root.assign(ref, UTILITIES[name]());
    return ref;
  };

  multident = function(code, tab) {
    code = code.replace(/\n/g, '$&' + tab);
    return code.replace(/\s+$/, '');
  };

}).call(this);
